*udisks-1.0.3-r1 (05 Jul 2011)

  05 Jul 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +udisks-1.0.3-r1.ebuild,
  +files/udisks-1.0.3-mkfs-tempdir.patch:
  Use /tmp instead of /var/run/udisks wrt #333893 by Diego Elio Pettenò.

*udisks-1.0.3 (30 Jun 2011)

