  Version bump.

  08 Jun 2011; Sebastian Pipping <sping@gentoo.org> udisks-1.0.2-r4.ebuild:
  Add >=sys-fs/udev-171[gudev] as an alternative dependency to
  >=sys-fs/udev-147[extras] (bug #370283)

*udisks-1.0.2-r4 (07 Jun 2011)

